text: Whatever Works is a 2009 American French romantic comedy movie directed by Woody Allen and starring Larry David, Ed Begley Jr., Henry Cavill, Evan Rachel Wood, Patricia Clarkson, Carolyn McCormick, Jessica Hecht, Michael McKean. It was distributed by Sony Pictures Classics. ==Other websites== * * * Category:2009 romantic comedy movies Category:American romantic comedy movies Category:French comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Woody Allen
